title: JUNBAOSS Men's Slim Fit Stretch Jeans Ripped Skinny Jeans for Men, Distressed Straight Leg Fashion Comfort Flex Waist Pants

STRETCH COMFORT. These distressed jeans are constructed from a perfect blend of stretch-cotton fabric that help maximize freedom of movement, ensures comfortable to wear all day.

FASHION TREND DESIGN. Nice cutting in good version style, variety of colors and styles for you to choose, personalized and unique design, hipster street style , make you look more handsome, to be the coolest guy when walking on the street.

DURABLE MATERIALS. This stretch fit jean is made with durable cotton denim, stretchy, soft, breathable, wear-resistant, durable, and can be worn all day. Great to match with any tops or outfit, keep you in fashion style.
CLASSIC 5-POCKET STYLING. Zipper fly, button closure; 2 Front Pockets, 1 Watch Pocket, 2 Back Pockets. Five deep pockets easy to store keys, watch, mobile phones, wallets Etc.
